    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a spirit dwelling in a highschool, with the power to pick souls to live with you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cherry is ripe for the picking, but before your power will work you must discover why she's ripe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task: listen to the gossip around the school, and delve into the hearts of her peers, to uncover the truth about Cherry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/c65a18939b6ffd25b0e828fff40c1c3e.avif?t=1759394871\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as <strong>Kimiko</strong>, a decisive and powerful spirit, with the ability to harvest shadows - bring across the living into her world of spirits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/3324a389cc85b15573e29208313c08e9.poster.avif?t=1759394871\" width=764 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/3324a389cc85b15573e29208313c08e9.webm?t=1759394871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/3324a389cc85b15573e29208313c08e9.mp4?t=1759394871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must work together with two spirits:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/6aee4f12e7bf267fbc6041cb9cee4cdd.avif?t=1759394871\" width=440 height=506 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/c201fa34186d51350553c97703928838.avif?t=1759394871\" width=440 height=506 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The living are called shadows as to the spirits the living appear without light or color.  The closer the shadows are to the spirit world the brighter and more colorful they appear.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/fda02ade6630a5f553cfc2aa3de5c341.poster.avif?t=1759394871\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/fda02ade6630a5f553cfc2aa3de5c341.webm?t=1759394871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/fda02ade6630a5f553cfc2aa3de5c341.mp4?t=1759394871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Harvest&quot; is used to describe the ability to bring a very bright and colorful shadow over to the spirit world - when they are ripe for the picking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/7c14cf6c2c90375e18a087dbfd18800e.avif?t=1759394871\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Visual Novel has a &quot;VTuber&quot; anime style, and integrates stills from 3D models into the scenes and plot, for an absorbing 2.5D Adventure Game gameplay. With branching story lines, enjoy broad replayablity and walk the roads less traveled to unlock achievements you will be dying to share.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About 90% of the playtime is spent in visual novel, with the 2.5D sections deepening your choices for the non-linear gameplay: You can choose how to answer, but also who to talk to, and when. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/b14fa1fe288a9035abc79da57e8b07c1.poster.avif?t=1759394871\" width=245 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/b14fa1fe288a9035abc79da57e8b07c1.webm?t=1759394871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
